### Register a new user
POST https://localhost:7001/api/Auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User"
}

###
### Login an existing user
POST https://localhost:7001/api/Auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

###
### Create a new Role (e.g., Admin)
POST https://localhost:7001/api/Roles/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roleName": "Admin"
}

###
### Assign a Role to a User
# IMPORTANT: You'll need to manually get the UserId from the Register or Login response
# and replace the GUID below with the actual UserId.
POST https://localhost:7001/api/Roles/assign-to-user
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "REPLACE_WITH_ACTUAL_USER_GUID_FROM_REGISTER_OR_LOGIN_RESPONSE",
  "roleName": "Admin"
}

###